   "source": [
    "# DataOverview — C. elegans Project (local inspection)\n",
    "**Purpose:** programmatic local inventory + safe previews of the datasets in this folder.  \n",
    "Run cells in order. Nothing here will access the network or modify data except to write a small `data_inventory.csv` summary in the notebook folder.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Workflow:**\n",
    "1. Build an inventory (file list + sizes)\n",
    "2. Show top-level folder summaries\n",
    "3. Search & list \"interesting\" files (connectome/EM/mesh/atlas formats)\n",
    "4. Safe preview small tabular files (csv/xlsx/json)\n",
    "5. Provide loaders for edge lists and HDF5/MAT files\n",
    "6. Summarize next recommended actions\n"
   ]
  },
