  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "5435a275",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "Phase3:"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "3745a563",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "PCA/t-SNE worked well for tier clustering despite low explained variance in PCA (suggests nonlinear structure captured by t-SNE). Kruskal-Wallis effective for nonparametric ANOVA on tiers. Z-score outliers robust. Partial Spearman with confound residualization (via projection matrix) astonishingly efficient for large-scale correlations, handling NaNs/low N. Stability via BH-FDR. Simulations for expr/meta/lit ingenious for testing. Fuzzy column detection/pivoting in resolvers handled varied formats well."
   ]
  },
